<i>adjective</i>: 왼손잡이 <i>noun</i>: 왼손잡이 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>왼손잡이</dt><br>
<dd>using or intended for the left hand</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: left-handed, sinistral, southpaw</dd><br>
</li>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>왼손잡이</dt><br>
<dd>a baseball pitcher who throws the ball with the left hand</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: southpaw, left-hander, left-handed pitcher, left hander, lefthander, lefty</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
